<h2 class="text-title">Space between columns</h2>

<p>This use a border-left on cols except the first. Avoid it if possible and use a padding inside the col.</p>

<div class="row spaced align-center">
    <div class="col wp-50" style="background: #AAF">50%</div>
    <div class="col wp-50" style="background: #AFA; border-color: red">50%</div>
</div>
<br>
<div class="row spaced align-center">
    <div class="col wp-33" style="background: #AAF">33%</div>
